Key Benefits of -v:
Real-time Feedback: Shows scan completion time estimates.
Faster Insight: Displays open ports as they are found, rather than waiting for the end of the scan.
Troubleshooting: Essential for diagnosing network issues or unexpected scan results.
Interactive Control: During a scan, you can press v or V to increase or decrease verbosity.








